      <title>工党谨慎争取英国权力 避免艰难经济抉择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/labour-s-cautious-pitch-for-uk-power-ducks-hard-economic-choices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 谨慎地阐述了该党的执政计划，重点关注增长和安全，优先保持英国民意调查中的领先优势，同时回避一旦掌权将不得不做出的艰难经济抉择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/labour-s-cautious-pitch-for-uk-power-ducks-hard-economic-choices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:46:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普告诉共和党，他计划彻底推翻拜登的电动汽车政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/trump-tells-gop-he-plans-to-entirely-reverse-biden-s-ev-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据参加此次私人会议的议员透露，唐纳德·特朗普在周四与众议院共和党人的会议上严厉批评了总统乔·拜登的电动汽车政策，并表示如果他在 11 月入主白宫，他将取消这些政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/trump-tells-gop-he-plans-to-entirely-reverse-biden-s-ev-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:39:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提出提高关税以抵消部分所得税减免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/trump-floats-tariffs-hikes-to-offset-some-income-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普提出通过提高关税来支付部分所得税减免的想法，此举将在美国国会明年讨论税法改革之际给全球贸易和消费者价格带来不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/trump-floats-tariffs-hikes-to-offset-some-income-tax-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:35:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳提交新的债务重组提案以推进债券持有人谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/ghana-sends-new-debt-rework-proposal-to-advance-bondholder-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加纳向该国国际债券持有人提交了一份新的债务重组提案，旨在推进重新制定 130 亿美元欧洲债券的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/ghana-sends-new-debt-rework-proposal-to-advance-bondholder-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫提名克里斯蒂·戈德史密斯·罗梅罗担任联邦存款保险公司 (FDIC) 董事长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/white-house-picks-christy-goldsmith-romero-for-new-fdic-chair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查发现了银行监管机构存在骚扰和歧视的可信指控后，白宫将提名克里斯蒂·戈德史密斯·罗梅罗接任联邦存款保险公司负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/white-house-picks-christy-goldsmith-romero-for-new-fdic-chair</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普对南非政府与非洲人国民大会和民主联盟的合作表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/s-p-skeptical-of-south-african-government-tie-up-between-anc-da</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标普全球评级表示，由于非国大内部未能就此类合作达成一致，由非洲人国民大会和民主联盟组成的南非政府可能会不稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/s-p-skeptical-of-south-african-government-tie-up-between-anc-da</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:01:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球调查显示三分之一消费者因加沙战争抵制品牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/more-consumers-choose-brands-based-on-politics-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份追踪战争、分裂选举和其他挑战对企业影响的新报告显示，消费者在做出购买决策时越来越多地考虑政治因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/more-consumers-choose-brands-based-on-politics-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
